title: Product Key Explorer v4.0.5.0 incl Patch - Crackingpatching
description:
Description: 
Product Key Explorer is a functional software that helps you find all the keys of installed software on your PC or PCs connected to the network. With this software, you can retrieve a lost license and then save it either in notepad or Excel file for future use.Regarding its use is very simple. simply click on "Find Keys and the list of all keys present on your PC instantly displayed in a list. Also, if you want to explore and find the keys found on other computers, click on "Select Computers" to choose them.Using this keyfinder lets you track the number of software installed in your business and every key has a centralized backup in a specific location. This is ideal for network administrators and business operators which adheres on software license policy.Checking out Tom's Guide for more Windows Applications and Windows Information.And if you have any questions or need some help regarding any tech issues, you may visit the Tom's Guide forums to help you out.
